Thread termination
--
When we can interrupt a thread

1 - if a thread is executing method that throws interupted exception
2 - if the threads code is handling the interupt signl explicitly


Demon Threds
--

Background threads that do not prevent the application from existing if the main thread terminates
(What ever happens inside the demon thread should not cause to main program to exist)
